query:
SELECT s.id, s.registrationNumber, s.fullName, se.subjectId, se.userId, sub.name as subjectName
FROM students s
INNER JOIN subjectEnrollments se ON se.studentId = s.id
LEFT JOIN subjects sub ON sub.id = se.subjectId
LIMIT 10;
